title: GTA V 100% guide v3.1.1
description:
Walkthrough for the acclaimed game by Rockstar Games. This is a step by step walkthrough guide with some additional features.

GTA 5 (GTA V / Grand Theft Auto V / Grand Theft Auto Five) is the fifth numbered game in the Grand Theft Auto series from developer Rockstar Games.

FEATURES:

- The complete Walkthroughs (with images and video!!)
- A guide to complete the game 100% (with all stunt jumps, all spaceship parts, all letter scraps)
- Importants tips to dominate in online game!
- The GTA 5 Interactive Map: a Google-style map anyone can edit or add too. It includes Collectibles, Stunt Jumps and much, much more.
- All the Cheats (PS3 and XBOX 360) and the Secrets to help Michael, Frenklin and Trevor
- How to Make Easy Money in GTA 5
- All the Achievements and Trophies (offline and online): you can check those completed

Here is a un-official 100% FAN-Guide including tips and tricks.You may find some information useful here.This is a perfect for beginner and intermediate player.
Please note - This is not a game !! It's is game guide.

- Add new guide for online trophies
